# DokcerDB2 V10.5
***dockerdocker-compose*** [dockerdocker-compose](https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45494811)
## 
``` bash
#oracledocker-compose.yml
version: '3'
services:
  oracle:
    image: registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/helowin/oracle_11g:latest
    container_name: oracle_db
    environment:
      ORACLE_PWD: "123456789"  #  Oracle  SYS 
    ports:
      - "1521:1521"  #  Oracle  1521 
    volumes:
      - oracle_data:/opt/oracle/oradata  #  Oracle 
    restart: always
volumes:
  oracle_data:

```
## 
registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/helowin/oracle_11g:latest
``` bash
#
docker load -i oracle_11g.tar
#tag
docker tag obca  registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/helowin/oracle_11g:latest
```
## 
``` bash
#
docker-compose up -d 
#
docker exec -it oracle_db bash
export ORACLE_HOME=/home/oracle/app/oracle/product/11.2.0/dbhome_2
export PATH=$ORACLE_HOME/bin:$PATH
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$ORACLE_HOME/lib
export ORACLE_SID=helowin
sqlplus / as sysdba
ALTER USER SYS IDENTIFIED BY "123456789";
```
